[Amit Varma]: If you enjoyed listening to this episode, hop on over to your nearest bookstore online or offline

03:14:41.300 --> 03:14:45.700
[Amit Varma]: and pick up Rumours of Spring by Farah Bashir. You can follow Farah on Twitter

03:14:45.700 --> 03:14:51.220
[Amit Varma]: at Farah Bashir, that's one word. You can follow me on Twitter at Amit Verma, A-M-I-T-V-A-R-M-A.

